OL,3,CRecruitment challenges 'a concern' for
OL,4,CChannel Island beauty businesses
OL,6,FChannel Island hair and beauty
OL,7,Fbusinesses are raising concerns about
OL,8,Fa recruitment and retention crisis
OL,9,Ffacing the sector.
OL,11,FThe sector was one of the worst hit by
OL,12,Fthe pandemic - and the high cost of
OL,13,Fliving in the Channel Islands has only
OL,14,Fadded to the recruitment problem as
OL,15,Fjob seekers search for roles in
OL,16,Ftradionally higher paid industries,
OL,17,Fsuch as finance.
