OL,3,CRecruitment challenges 'a concern' for
OL,4,CChannel Island beauty businesses
OL,6,FAnna Lewandowska, who runs Glamour
OL,7,FHouse beauty salon in St Helier, said:
OL,8,F"There is just no chance. Recently, we
OL,9,Flost two staff members and it's really
OL,10,Fhard. I have to be here 12 hours a day
OL,11,Fto ensure I can pay the wages and the
OL,12,Fbills.
OL,14,F"I'm very happy to take students and
OL,15,Fspend time with them to teach them
OL,16,Ffrom the top to the bottom."
