OL,3,CRecruitment challenges 'a concern' for
OL,4,CChannel Island beauty businesses
OL,6,FA 2022 report by the National Hair and
OL,7,FBeauty Federation revealed unfilled
OL,8,Fvacancies in 57% of UK hair and beauty
OL,9,Fbusinesses, with more than half taking
OL,10,Fover 16 weeks to fill.
OL,12,FHowever, there is reason to be
OL,13,Foptimistic for the future, as
OL,14,FHighlands College has recently seen an
OL,15,Fincrease in students applying to study
OL,16,Fits courses in Hair and Beauty.
