OL,3,CRecruitment challenges 'a concern' for
OL,4,CChannel Island beauty businesses
OL,6,FHead of Hair and Beauty, Pawel Kulon,
OL,7,Ftold ITV News: "We're trying to meet
OL,8,Fthe industry demands. We train a lot
OL,9,Fof people - and this year is
OL,10,Fexceptional as we have got some of the
OL,11,Fhighest numbers of students we've ever
OL,12,Fhad on our hair and beauty courses."
OL,14,FThe college is also partnering with
OL,15,FJersey secondary schools to offer
OL,16,Fstudents practical training in beauty
OL,17,Ftherapy from an earlier point in their
OL,18,Feducation.
